,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"戶b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"學b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad267f46754af9c424b56dca01513a72d60a5e4","tid":2169471,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de47af6b918a4bcab90f22a0e64d4901d11b63ae","tid":2169471,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/K5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FK5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=61d729fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FK5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ%2F&h=25a0f8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/K5E2N6TX5NFOJN6BGQR4JUR5EQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭國泉今年６月23日在何君堯等陪同下舉行記招，稱對許智峯提私人檢控感「莫名其妙」。他指網上流傳片段可見他當時被黑衣人襲擊，形容自己承受沉重的心理負擔，「覺得呢個司法制度唔公平。」何君堯則批評許智峯無理控告，形容情況是「原告變被告」，更質疑謂如證據夠強，「點解警方唔提檢控呢？」他指提私人檢控是「越俎代庖」，檢控決定應交還律政司 ，「唔可以畀許智峯胡作妄為。」身兼律師的何君堯並為鄭國泉提供法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n被鄭國泉撞斷雙腳的23歲女子，至今仍未康復。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯與同父異母的兄長何君柱一樣是律師，後者設有何君柱律師樓，由他做首席合夥人，何君堯屬高級合夥人。該律師樓專做土地交易、樓宇買賣。公司網站另有「我們之友」，為胞弟何君達的匯領會計師事務所宣傳。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"何己完同餅強咁老友，知唔少國家秘密，點解照肺無佢份？"},{"pid":"aa69de651dc5b8654d7e426c32304947612c3ffb","tid":2169471,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb557a2240b78a92a3faa2480766585ffa600929","tid":2169471,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58dd89ef7bef9217dee4507114cd8a759be8f2a0","tid":2169471,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72426224547a77cab5c7910d66d323747d8ed281","tid":2169471,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:42:17.000Z","msg"